      </p>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <!-- Article 1 - Jul 9, 2026 -->
        <a href="/es/news/blog-chitek-ahf-advantages" class="group bg-white rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-border-light hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col md:flex-row no-underline">
          <div class="relative w-full md:w-[320px] lg:w-[380px] h-48 md:h-auto bg-gradient-to-br from-brand-orange/10 to-brand-orange/5 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
